<template>
  <router-view/>
</template>
<script>
import request from "@/utils/request";

export default {
  data() {
    return {
      currentId: sessionStorage.getItem("currentId")
    }
  },
  watch: {
    currentId(newVal, oldVal) {
// 当currentId变化时执行某个函数
      this.cleanup()
    }
  },
  methods: {
    cleanup() {
      request.get("/file/delete", {
        params: {
          UserId:sessionStorage.getItem("currentId")
        }}).then(res => {
        console.log(res)
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
<style>

</style>
